Class SimpleLiteral

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.SimpleLiteral
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Literal, Value
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanLiteral, CalendarLiteral, DecimalLiteral, IntegerLiteral, LiteralImpl, MemLiteral, NativeLiteral, NumericLiteral

    public class SimpleLiteral
extends Object
implements Literal
